author: Nexcell Pride
text:
Another great streaming ever... And again with that BGM which identifies Rushia-hime :_るんるん:

A Best marathonic Baseball event, when our new "Princess Nine" (Reference of 1998 Anime series) demonstrated she is good at baseball, until she encountered with worldwide gamer who defeated her 9 - 0. Despite result, she never raged up. :_ハート:
The another results were only clutches, but the bonus track were Toyboxing (Draw) and Reversi (Victory) :_ちょうちょ:

1 hour and 40 minutes of normal streaming, but the best part was the Supaachaato Orei Time (4 hours and 18 minutes of Superchat reading, and Rushia-hime forgot again to display the logo of "Supacha Yomi Time" or "Supaachaato Orei Time" for unknown reasons) when again red hearts on LiveChat were the main protagonist, and we saw Rushia smiling again. Also the word "kawaii" (japanese word for "cute") was present into LiveChat.

Once more, Rushia-hime demonstrated being more cute and lovely as always, even more.
Definitively is the girl of the moment. :_きゅん:
